WEBVTT

00:00:11.293 --> 00:00:13.561
Yengil, yorqin va quvnoq.

00:00:13.561 --> 00:00:17.881
XVIII asr boshining eng tanish
navolaridan biri.

00:00:17.881 --> 00:00:21.371
Uni sanoqsiz filmlar va reklama
roliklarida eshitish mumkin.

00:00:21.371 --> 00:00:24.630
ammo bu qanday musiqa,
va nega u shunday yangraydi?

00:00:24.630 --> 00:00:27.462
Bu italyan bastakori Antonio Vivaldi
qalamiga mansub

00:00:27.462 --> 00:00:30.803
"To'rt mavsum" dan
"Bahor" konsertining kirish qismi.